182
00:12:26,102 --> 00:12:30,067
Je to Adachi, pre božie zmilovanie!

183
00:12:31,708 --> 00:12:33,154
VIEŠ ČO?

184
00:12:33,837 --> 00:12:35,380
Pozorne ma počúvaj.

185
00:12:37,915 --> 00:12:43,423
